headline: J.B. Hunt upgraded to Positive from Neutral at Susquehanna
summary: Susquehanna upgraded J.B. Hunt (JBHT) to Positive from Neutral with a price target of $240, up from $160. The firm believes the company will benefit from better truckload contract rates and volume tailwinds in intermodal.
